data.description: Beautiful John Houston home located in the highly coveted Shannon Creek neighborhood. This is a corner lot home that will have wonderful backyard views of the Shannon Creek park that will be located in the natural wooded lot behind the home. This four bed three full bath two story offers a large open plan, high ceilings, a large kitchen with custom cabinets, granite countertops, large owner's suite and oversized shower, a formal dining, separate study and covered patio for entertaining. This is a large home that has the space to entertain and build forever memories. Don't miss out on this beautiful home!
